=\"center\">3800,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">1750,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">500,00 грн. + 100$</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">50$ + 50 євро</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">2586,00 грн. + 200$</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">600,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">600,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">1000,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">150,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">550,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>44200,00 грн. +350</strong><strong>$</strong><strong> + 50 євро</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">55083,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">21450,00 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">3468,05 грн.</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>-</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"ce